data.title: Darlington Borough Council - Housing
data.text:
We provide a housing service and can tell you everything you need to know about applying for a Council home, paying your rent, and how we can help if things go wrong. Our website can provide information on:

welfare reform

money, debt and benefits

home energy

independence for older and disabled people

nuisance and anti-social behaviour

council improvements

private sector housing

rent a garage

housing benefits

bee wise money advice service

customer engagement

mutual exchange

red hall regeneration

providers of social and affordable rented homes

home energy

discussing your tenancy
